race.comment: Good race with good pace and most of the leading chances will be up there. RESTRICTED ACCESS (2) has been racing in great form, the latest leading throughout for a big win here last time. Looks the one to run down again. WITHIN SIGHT (5) ran on well to place fresh then got home hard to score at Launceston latest. Will be stalking the main bunch and prove tough to hold out again. STEELE MY SUNSHINE (9) was a deserved winner last time and another who can be finishing on with the right run. GINGERSON (4) is finding it hard to break through this time in but not far away, placing three of last four include g the latest over 1430m at this track. Has a good record course and distance and senior rider aboard. With plenty of pace will give a sight again.
